@startuml fallback-knowledge-capture
!include _standard-style.puml

title Fallback Knowledge Capture (No Agents) - Sequence Diagram

actor Developer as Dev
participant "Coding CLI" as System
participant "ukb-cli" as UKB
database "Knowledge Base" as KB

Dev -> System: coding --copilot
System -> System: Check API keys
System --> Dev: No API keys found

Dev -> UKB: ukb --interactive
UKB -> Dev: Enter problem description
Dev -> UKB: "Handle async React errors"
UKB -> Dev: Enter solution
Dev -> UKB: "Use error boundaries"
UKB -> Dev: [Additional prompts...]
UKB -> KB: Write to shared-memory.json
KB --> UKB: Updated
UKB --> Dev: Knowledge captured

Dev -> System: vkb
System -> Dev: Opens web viewer
Dev -> Dev: Browse knowledge graph

@enduml